.TH "ata_wait_after_reset" 9 "ata_wait_after_reset" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ata_wait_after_reset \- wait for link to become ready after reset
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" ata_wait_after_reset
.BI "(struct ata_link *link "  ","
.BI "unsigned long deadline "  ","
.BI "int (*check_ready)(struct ata_link *link) "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "link" 12
link to be waited on
.IP "deadline" 12
deadline jiffies for the operation
.IP "check_ready" 12
callback to check link readiness

Wait for \fIlink\fP to become ready after reset.

LOCKING:
EH context.
.SH "RETURN"
0 if \fIlink\fP is ready before \fIdeadline\fP; otherwise, -errno.
